pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Bayanan da aka nuna akan wannan dashboard ana tattara su kai tsaye daga martanin bincike kuma baya zuwa daga kididdigar ƙasa ko saitin bayanai. Yana wakiltar ra'ayoyin da matasa suka bayyana a lokacin binciken, kuma duk wani sakamako da aka zana daga waɗannan martanin alhakin mai amfani ne, ba PMNCH ba. PMNCH ta himmatu wajen mutuntawa, haɓakawa da kuma kare haƙƙi da jin daɗin kowane ɗaiɗai. Duk wani ra'ayi da aka bayyana a cikin martanin binciken ko kayan da aka buga da ke fitowa daga wannan dashboard wanda ya saba wa wannan alƙawarin PMNCH bai amince da shi ba.

pmn01a-subtext: Barka da zuwa "Abin da Matasa ke So" Dashboard! Wannan kayan aikin haɗin gwiwar yana ba da wakilci na gani na martani da fahimtar da muke tattarawa daga matasa masu shekaru 10-24 a duniya. Jigon shirin shine tambaya mai buɗewa: "Don inganta jin daɗina, ina so ...". Matasa daga ko'ina cikin duniya suna amsa wannan, suna ba mu haske na musamman game da buƙatunsu, fatansu, da burinsu. Bincika bayanan, gano labaran da ke bayan lambobi, kuma ku kasance tare da mu don faɗaɗa muryoyin matasa biliyan 1.8 a duniya. Don ƙarin koyo game da yaƙin neman zaɓe, ziyarci http://www.1point8.org.
